---
title: Chicken and Sweetcorn Soup with crunchy cheese crostini
description: There's something endlessly comforting about the classic combination of chicken and sweetcorn, and this recipe is no different. A creamy texture and herbaceous undertone combine to create added depth while the accompanying cheesy crostini add a satisfying bite to an all-round delicious dish.
